HEADWORD: Fathead
<hw>Fat"head`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A cyprinoid fish of the Mississippi valley
(<spn>Pimephales promelas</spn>); -- called also <altname>black-headed
minnow</altname>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A labroid food fish of
California; the redfish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

